<br>
If I remember correctly, most of the parses that had been posted were by level 60 characters. <br>
<br>
At level 60, BO IV + Muzzle seemed to stack properly.<br>
<br>
Also at level 60 Ancient Burnout Blaze + Muzzle seemed to have reached a cap, and players were better off not casting the muzzle.<br>
<br>
I haven't seen anything regarding haste caps since the level cap was increased.<br>
